@NODE Intro "Introduction"

@{u}@{b}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}

EasyEncode is a GUI for mp2/mp3 encoder like @{"MusicIn" link programs} or @{"mp3enc" link programs}. It should make your  live much easier, because you haven't no longer to handle all these cli-paramers of that programs. EasyEncode gives you an nice GUI for it.
With EasyEncode you can also convert audio-mpegs layer 3 to layer 2 or stereo to mono-mpegs.
@ENDNODE

@NODE Copyright "Copyright"

@{u}@{b}Copyright@{uu}@{ub}

EasyEncode is @{"Giftware" link Giftware}.

It is only allowed to copy the whole archive (programfile + this guide).

Use it on your own risk.

@ENDNODE


